Title Review: A proposal to implement the total ban in an innovative way Why is the total ban not to be gradually applied at the governorate level  so that it affects the course of life in Bahrain. A plan can be developed to include all governorates every time period that includes one or two governorates  so an alert is sent a week before to alert the residents of the governorate to prepare for the total ban for a period of two weeks  and the rest of the governorates will be in the normal situation during the ban period  so it is possible to limit all cases at the governorate level and after that  entry of any governorate population is prohibited. The second is to ensure that no new cases are created. In this way  it is possible within one month to contain all cases in Bahrain if the ban is applied to two governorates at the same time.
content: A proposal to implement the total ban in an innovative way Why is the total ban not to be gradually applied at the governorate level  so that it affects the course of life in Bahrain  A plan can be developed to include all governorates every time period that includes one or two governorates  so an alert is sent a week before to alert the residents of the governorate to prepare for the total ban for a period of two weeks  and the rest of the governorates will be in the normal situation during the ban period  so it is possible to limit all cases at the governorate level and after that  entry of any governorate population is prohibited  The second is to ensure that no new cases are created  In this way  it is possible within one month to contain all cases in Bahrain if the ban is applied to two governorates at the same time
